        </div>
		<div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-offset="300" data-aos-easing="ease-in-sine" class="col-md-6">
			<p class="lead">
				Phone: +1 519 729-5554
				<br/>
				Email: shreyas.srivatsa@uwaterloo.ca
			</p>
			<span class="lead">Connect with me!</span>
			<a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/Shreyas15srivatsa" title="Github" 
			   class="btn btn-dark btn-lg fa fa-github" aria-hidden="true"></a>
			<a target="_blank" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/shreyas-srivatsa-828745161/" title="LinkedIn" 
